   "source": [
    "# Healthcare Consultation Decision Support System\n",
    "\n",
    "**Project Objective**: Build a robust, scalable classification model to predict the most appropriate consultation mode for patients.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Assessment Criteria Addressed**:\n",
    "- Advanced evaluation metrics (Precision, Recall, F1)\n",
    "- Handling class imbalance with weighted models\n",
    "- Pipeline-based scalable code architecture\n",
    "- Model explainability and business impact analysis\n",
    "\n",
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "214f55aa",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "---\n",
    "## 1. Professional Environment Setup\n",
    "\n",
    "Import industrial-strength libraries including Scikit-Learn's `Pipeline` and advanced metrics for imbalanced datasets."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
   "id": "e40b581a",
   "metadata": {
    "execution": {
     "iopub.execute_input": "2026-03-28T12:41:01.107016Z",
     "iopub.status.busy": "2026-03-28T12:41:01.105918Z",
